headline: WM to Host 2025 Investor Day on June 24
summary: HOUSTON, March 04, 2025--WM (NYSE: WM) announced that it will host an investor day on Tuesday, June 24, beginning at 9 a.m. EST, at the New York Stock Exchange in New York City.
